commit.message: CI against MRI 2.4.0, MRI 2.2.6 and JRuby 9.1.7.0 (#56)
Provide an exception class and message as arguments to raise
Use the new Ruby 1.9 hash syntax
Drop support for Ruby versions less than 2.2.2
Use a guard clause instead of wrapping the code inside a conditional expression
Gem oga should appear before ox in their gem group
Favor a normal unless-statement over a modifier clause in a multiline statement
Add test for parsing frozen string and fixed related bug (#52)
